My exact pattern can not be replicated by most. Transparency is impossible for some - dirty, morally compromised, embarrassed/ashamed, scared. Hence it just won't work.

what can be replicated by anyone is documentation discipline.

For researchers/opponents/gov: only some actually understand what's happening. The full footprint tells the whole story.


